#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:140
msgid "Contributing"
msgstr "贡献"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:142
msgid ""
"LMCache Frontend is an open-source project and we welcome contributions "
"from the community! Whether you want to fix bugs, add new features, "
"improve documentation, or share ideas, your contributions are "
"appreciated."
msgstr "LMCache 前端是一个开源项目，我们欢迎社区的贡献！无论您想修复错误、添加新功能、改善文档还是分享想法，我们都非常感谢您的贡献。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:146
msgid "Ways to contribute:"
msgstr "贡献方式："

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:148
msgid ""
"**Report Issues**: Found a bug or have a feature request? Open an issue "
"on GitHub."
msgstr "**报告问题**：发现了一个错误或有功能请求？在 GitHub 上提交一个问题。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:150
msgid ""
"**Submit Pull Requests**: Fork the repository, make your changes, and "
"submit a PR."
msgstr "**提交拉取请求**：分叉仓库，进行更改，并提交 PR。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:152
msgid "**Improve Documentation**: Help us make the docs clearer and more helpful."
msgstr "**改善文档**：帮助我们使文档更清晰、更有帮助。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:153
msgid ""
"**Share Feedback**: Let us know how you're using LMCache Frontend and "
"what could be improved."
msgstr "**分享反馈**：让我们知道您如何使用 LMCache 前端以及可以改进的地方。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:156
msgid "Join us in making LMCache Frontend better for everyone!"
msgstr "加入我们，让 LMCache Frontend 变得更好！"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:160
msgid "More Information"
msgstr "更多信息"

#: ../../source/production/observability/frontend.rst:162
msgid ""
"For more details, visit the `LMCache Frontend GitHub repository "
"<https://github.com/LMCache/lmcache_frontend>`_."
msgstr "有关更多详细信息，请访问 `LMCache Frontend GitHub 仓库 <https://github.com/LMCache/lmcache_frontend>`_。"

